                    <H2>Public lottery for new recreational lots&nbsp; planned for summer</H2>
<P>Kluane First Nation and the Yukon government are developing 11 new&nbsp;recreational lots at Dutch Harbour on Kluane Lake. The lots&nbsp;will be available through a land lottery later this summer.</P>
<UL>
<LI><A title="Opens in this window" href="http://www.gov.yk.ca/news/16-141.html">Read the news release &gt;&gt;&gt;</A></LI></UL>
<P>
<HR>

<P></P>
<H2>Responsible oil and gas development</H2>
<P>We have added a new section to the Oil and Gas Resources&nbsp;website. This section explores the government's role in the responsible development of oil and gas in Yukon. In the coming months, we will build on these webpages, adding resources and more detailed information on this and related topics.</P>
<UL>
<LI><A title="Opens in this window" href="http://www.emr.gov.yk.ca/oilandgas/responsible-development-of-oil-and-gas.html">Check out the new resources &gt;&gt;&gt;</A></LI></UL>
<P>
<HR>

<P></P>
<H2><EM>Forest Resources Act</EM> 5 year review</H2>
<P>The Government of Yukon is beginning&nbsp;a review of the <EM>Forest Resources Act</EM>.&nbsp;The review&nbsp;presents the opportunity to ensure our forest legislation meets the needs of First Nations, industry and the public while protecting the health of our forests. </P>
<UL>
<LI><A title="Opens in this window" href="http://www.gov.yk.ca/news/16-061.html">Read the news release &gt;&gt;&gt;</A> </LI>
<LI><A title="Opens in this window" href="http://www.emr.gov.yk.ca/forestry/5-year-review-of-Forest-Resources-Act.html">Learn more about the review of the <EM>Forest Resources Act</EM> &gt;&gt;&gt;</A> </LI></UL>
<P>
<P>
<HR>

<P></P>
<H2>News Releases</H2>
<P><STRONG><A title="Read news release in this window" href="http://www.gov.yk.ca/news/16-174.html" target="_blank">Minister recognizes mining week and new bedrock map technology</A> <BR><FONT color=#808080>May 5, 2016</FONT></STRONG> - Yukon Geological Survey's new digital bedrock geology map will assist exploration geologists.</P>

<P><STRONG><A title="Read news release in this window" href="http://www.gov.yk.ca/news/16-170.html" target="_blank">New comprehensive report outlines geothermal heat and power potential in Yukon</A><BR><FONT color=#808080>May 4, 2016</FONT></STRONG> - Newly published favourability maps show Yukonâs potential for generating heat and power using geothermal energy.</P>
<P><STRONG><A title="Read the news release in this window" href="http://www.gov.yk.ca/news/16-148.html">Work on forestry road to continue near Haines Junction this summer</A> <BR><FONT color=#808080>April 20, 2016</FONT></STRONG> - The Mackintosh East Forest Resources Road will be surfaced for easier access.</P>
<UL>
<LI><A title="Open our news release page in this window" href="http://www.gov.yk.ca/news/emr.html">More news from Energy, Mines and Resources &gt;&gt;&gt;</A> </LI></UL>
